{"tid":938584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【蘋民直擊】尖沙嘴男女攀窗爬水渠逃走？ 男走甩女受傷","createTime":"2018-12-12T12:10:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T12:42:51.000Z","uid":47272,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"95c8c689bd84efbf2e6156f69e64677a570bf508","tid":938584,"uid":47272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T12:10:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181212&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59022130\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181212%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59022130&d=0cDfHLXBfj5lCtx6NEeU%2BwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=5d179369\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181212%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59022130&h=f72f34fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181212&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59022130</a><br />\n尖沙嘴發生男女墮樓事件，下午4時許，讀者途經寶勒巷2A對開時，赫見大廈外牆有一對男女正由2樓一單位攀窗而出，沿水渠爬落1樓，場面驚險。其間，該名男子走至一個招牌再躍下，跳至約3米下的街上離去。而另一名女子其後亦爬至1樓，見無路可逃亦躍至地面，墮地時疑受傷動彈不得。<br />\n讀者朱先生表示，當時首先見一名男子跳至街上，懷疑腳部受傷，一拐一拐離開現場，其後女子亦跳至地面，剛巧一名女途人經過，幸未有被壓中。朱生指出，事發大廈有不少一樓一鳳姐單位，估計是警方掃黃期間有人攀窗逃走。<br />\n警方表示，下午4時17分接獲一名途人報案，指發現一名29歲姓廖內地女子站於上址一單位外，其後從另一單位墮下至地下。警員接報到場，廖女清醒被送往伊利沙伯醫院治理。警方經初步調查，列有人意外受傷。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/vjwz2nhu\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvjwz2nhu&h=75479bc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/584anuvt\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F584anuvt&h=abca9ff1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4ab059bc8c756444405b701acc46618cd89831d7","tid":938584,"uid":54681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T12:17:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"777f8d84868e90861c5e51d8ec1b